ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectRemission Order in Respect of Fees for the Issuance of Passports, Certificates of Identity and Refugee Travel Documents (Alberta)
PrecisRemission Order in respect of FEES FOR THE ISSUANCE OF PASSPORTS, CERTIFICATES OF IDENTITY AND REFUGEE TRAVEL DOCUMENTS (ALBERTA) in order to remit the fee for replacing immigration and/or travel documents that were damaged or lost as a result of the massive flooding in Alberta in June 2013.
